        "action": "Replace bank holidays with increased statutory holiday entitlements",
        "additional_details": "",
        "background": "Bank holidays create road, rail and airport misery. We want the Government to get rid of them and replace them with additional statutory holiday entitlements. Most people would still have the same amount of time off work, but wouldn\u2019t all have to be off work on the same days.",
